<p class="para"><span class="sub-head1">c. Information Received. </span> The QSIPL may provide us with information about your Product, use of the Product, and use of Digital Content, other content, and the QSIPL Services (such as search queries, installed applications, viewing and usage data, and log files). Manufacturers of your Product may also provide us with similar information. Information provided to QSIPL may be processed in the cloud to improve your experience and our services, and may be stored on servers outside the country in which you live. We will handle any information we receive in accordance with the <a href="https://www.amazon.in/privacy">quicksecureindia.com Privacy Notice</a>. Please visit the Settings menu of your Product if you prefer to opt out of providing certain information.
